# Wollaston Hanks — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in real values for local development.
# In production (Vercel), set these variables in Project Settings → Environment Variables.

# Web3Forms Access Key (https://web3forms.com)
# Required for form submissions (Submit Opportunity + Contact) to deliver email.
# 1. Create a free Web3Forms account
# 2. Verify the recipient email (e.g. contact@wollastonhanks.com)
# 3. Copy the access key here
VITE_WEB3FORMS_KEY=your-web3forms-access-key
